  p    [$ git tag v1.4-lw]
  h3    Tagging later
  p    [$ git tag -a [tagName] [commit]] i.e.:
  p    [$ git tag -a v1.2 9fceb02]
  h3    Sharing Tags
  p    Just run: [$ git push origin [tagname]
  p    By default the [$ git push] command doesn’t transfer tags to remote servers.
  p    To push up at once a lot of tags you can use the:[$ git push --tags]
